Subject: [PATCH 659/909] arm64: dts: r8a77965-salvator-x: Enable ADSP

commit dff974f16d5a15a4dc0fe8a395c205bf9dcd7f17 from
git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/horms/renesas-bsp.git

This patch enables Audio DSP (ADSP) for the Salvator-X board
on the R8A77965 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Takeshi Kihara <takeshi.kihara.df@renesas.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a77965-salvator-x.dts | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a77965-salvator-x.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a77965-salvator-x.dts
index a0ee5c9d1033..d9fb0df70dab 100644
